events.marketingText:
​During the Fireside Chat, esteemed speakers from ICP.HUB HK will share their expertise and insights on the practical applications of Web3 technologies in Hong Kong. They will discuss the transformative power of decentralized blockchain systems and other cutting-edge applications at how they are reshaping industries. 

Moderator:
Kate Wong @STFIL
​Panel Speakers:
Ryan He @ICP.HUB HK
Monin @MUNG
Miffy Chan @Ozaru
Chris Fung @Yuliverse
​Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to learn from industry experts, celebrate the spirit of innovation, and connect with fellow enthusiasts.

About [Dynasty. ICP.HUB HK​](https://twitter.com/dynasty_icp)
Dynasty is ICP's official Hong Kong hub, created to incubate and accelerate the next wave of locally grown web3 protocols.

About [852Web3](https://twitter.com/852web3)
852Web3 is taking the first step in leading the cultural and community development in Hong Kong, and also a leading Web3 marketing agency in Asia.

​About [Ooosh Tech Lab​​](https://www.linkedin.com/company/ooosh-tech-lab/?originalSubdomain=hk)
Ooosh Tech Lab is an Integrated Venture Capital firm investing into the future of web and work. They build ecosystems with Co-working Space and Incubator for early-stage startups.

Moritz, Emil, Victor & Fabian
